sub_title: Director & Founder of The English Center
summary:
The English Center specializes in live-online Business English courses. We deliver top quality personal, small group, intensive and corporate training with a friendly style and a communicative approach to create Business English learning experiences that are empowering and effective. 

Our select team of British and American native-speaker trainers provide private business english lessons, executive communication training, English workshops, EnglishCentral.com + coach online, advanced Business English courses, customized lessons content, job interview preparation, business communications, presentations and public speaking, TOEIC preparation, complete language assessments, Oxford online level testing, speed courses, accent reduction/pronunciation training, second language stress reduction, translation services (Nederlands-English) and native copy & editing.
